And after the group tried to "expel an evil spirit" from the woman.
The isolation of "witches" supports the people here without regard to their education.
“The Standard” quoted a 42-year-old entrepreneur from Burkina Faso: “Fresh women of human souls are a danger earlier than today,” he said.
